{"tid":261944,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦火牛一年半內2隻都同一壞法代表咩？","createTime":"2017-05-29T00:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T11:33:45.000Z","uid":18788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2257c190401dbacd72289ff20c66ea9de4fdde10","tid":261944,"uid":18788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T00:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/29/081243_6d2877e9097d28c7d583e112be05a0d1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F29%2F081243_6d2877e9097d28c7d583e112be05a0d1.jpg&h=a0afc740&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n用緊悠二以前既呢條list，2次部腦都係開唔到機，一開佢著一著，之後自動熄，然後自動開，自動熄不停loop，第一次拎去整換左隻450w既，琴日又係咁壞法，想問下係部機有其他問題定隻純粹真係隻牛壞，定係個watt數唔夠做？要換既又換咩好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\np.s. 部腦平時靜係攞黎上網，睇戲，唔該晒"},{"pid":"9524607866421c93eb3d4e32d9dbdb76727f0a11","tid":261944,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T00:23:23.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f88f5ff4aaf1971b967752344acc9b4d937a899e","tid":261944,"uid":27330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T01:36:42.000Z","msg":"400w銅牛一定夠的 睇下有無野未插好 <br />\n自己loop開機 我都係拆哂佢再裝過就通常搞掂"},{"pid":"80c230bc16ed0826b3d6495c654fc35dbf481743","tid":261944,"uid":10904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T01:39:20.000Z","msg":"GX2 PRO<br />\n完<br />\n鑊氣牛黎"},{"pid":"c34f373b573ecd68a17d81f078ea2f90ade53c29","tid":261944,"uid":10904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T01:40:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>GX2 PRO<br />\n完<br />\n鑊氣牛黎</blockquote><br />\n無野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGX Storm先係<br />\nGX2pro呢隻唔係"},{"pid":"39a862e6c743e7f3157ed833a3e90b9aff4d77e2","tid":261944,"uid":10904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T01:41:49.000Z","msg":"一開一著好多問題都會咁<br />\n最簡單ram拆出黎刷下佢先"},{"pid":"6ad87f2a821db8f0f7d7cd965537cef4e8844873","tid":261944,"uid":18788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T02:51:49.000Z","msg":"唔該晒上面咁多位，等陣試下先"},{"pid":"415d56d151a98d793394988d50475d37ae9f1042","tid":261944,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:19:32.000Z","msg":"底板無上銅柱？感覺有d嘢漏電"},{"pid":"ee210d1a4b38d33dea3b57bc1838cd735eb7fd9d","tid":261944,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:32:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>底板無上銅柱？感覺有d嘢漏電</blockquote><br />\n似係呢個多d"},{"pid":"1421017b63c4f4bc4a6504237030aa62f60569f6","tid":261944,"uid":18788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T04:17:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>底板無上銅柱？感覺有d嘢漏電</blockquote><br />\n似係呢個多d</blockquote><br />\n可以點check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇圖可以對下 我部機係出面砌的"},{"pid":"c2878e426044b1eafdc7f9504e522adcb2a4dc11","tid":261944,"uid":18788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:06:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>底板無上銅柱？感覺有d嘢漏電</blockquote><br />\n似係呢個多d</blockquote><br />\n可以點check<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有冇圖可以對下 我部機係出面砌的</blockquote><br />\n同埋係咪有野漏電導致火牛壞定點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55462c386073b3d6a573a620dcda93ec5ad06845","tid":261944,"uid":18788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:47:33.000Z","msg":"btw 我部機係中央田砌左兩年，好似要自己拎隻火牛比代理整，但佢會唔會幫你砌番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋cooler master牛有幾耐保養？"},{"pid":"5fb075cc91c7574a3d28c4559c5e7a01ae4c91c6","tid":261944,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:50:39.000Z","msg":"買隻靚少少，反正可以帶落下部機用"},{"pid":"9e85c76ffa803a